# Tic Tac Toe Game

## Overview

This project is a simple Tic Tac Toe game implemented using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. It provides a responsive design and allows two players to take turns making moves.

## Features

- Two-player game
- Responsive design
- Win and draw detection
- Reset game functionality
- Implemented with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript
- Easy to integrate and customize

